"Today the Egyptian people laid the foundation of new life — absolute freedom, a genuine democracy and stability" — Morsi, the 60-year-old engineer with an American education from "Muslim Brotherhood", fundamentalist group which the most part from 84 years of the existence was the forbidden organization serving as a target for rigid actions of the governments replacing each other declared.
