On October 31 the Moscow City Court decided to recognize invalid the license about registration of Rosbalt agency, - "Tape" writes.
Drew Roskomnadzor on deprivation of agency of the status of mass media - for systematic and gross violations of the law on mass media.
During process unpleasant precedent was created: the court counted possible to close mass media, having actually refused to the edition the right to put forward counterarguments.
What is "Rosbalt"
JSC Rosbalt News Agency was founded in St. Petersburg in 2000.
In the next years the agency opened the second head office in Moscow and a number of regional divisions.
Also representations in the countries of the former USSR work for agency.
Since 2001 "Rosbalt" developed and functioned as federal information and analytical agency.
