Thus "Rosbalt" always occupied quite specific niche: notes with reference to sources in law enforcement agencies were the center of exclusive publications of agency (and make still).
Talk on proximity of the edition to power structures proceeded throughout existence of agency.
Along with that "Rosbalt" had extensive base of sources in various departments, such assumptions were spoken well also with that the project Natalya was at the head of Chaplin - Victor Cherkesov's wife.
