Syria destroyed the means of production of the chemical weapon, the supervisory group speaks
Syria destroyed the capital equipment for production of the chemical weapon and ammunition with the poisoning gas, the international supervisory group while violent confrontations stormed in the north of the country, near one of objects where as believe, toxic substances are stored declared on Thursday.
Also on Thursday the Syrian group of activists declared that more than 120 000 people were killed since the beginning of civil war in the country nearly three years ago.
