End of that is on the substance of an initial stage of destruction — an important milestone in the ambitious schedule which sets as the purpose to destroy all chemical weapon of Damascus to the middle of 2014.
Destruction of the equipment means that Syria cannot make the new chemical weapon more.
Nevertheless Damascus still should begin destruction of the existing weapon and stocks.
The country as believe, has about 1000 metric tons of chemicals and the weapon, including mustard gas and nerve gas sarin.
This statement was made during heavy fighting on Thursday in the city of Safira in which, according to experts, there is an object on production of the chemical weapon, and also a place of its storage, reports the Syrian center of protection of human rights which is based in Britain.
